---
title: "US39 — Personalised reminders + alerts (rule-based)"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Premium User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>NotificationsScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ManageNotificationPrefs
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Profile (prefs) · PlannedWorkout
  A->>B: enable personalised reminders
  B->>C: setEnabled(typeKey, true)
  C->>E: updateNotificationPrefs(userId, prefs)
  E-->>C: prefs saved
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (enabled)
  note over C: planned ScheduleReminder reads active plan<br/>workout times + rest days (rule-based, NOT AI)
  C->>E: scheduleReminder(plan times, rest days)
  E-->>C: scheduled
  B-->>A: reminders tuned to the plan
  note over E: updateNotificationPrefs via ProfileGateway (built) —<br/>scheduleReminder via NotificationGateway (planned, rule-based)
